{"type": "article", "id": 43649, "title": "自驾游时小朋友不耐烦的话，就来涂车吧｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2017-08-01T23:07:49Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 247, "name": "Nendo"}, {"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 42868, "name": "Women Talk Real Estate"}, {"id": 42869, "name": "Parallax"}, {"id": 29749, "name": "赫兹"}, {"id": 42870, "name": "Baxter and Bailey"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 9, "praise_count": 77, "image": "img/article/article_show/20170801184229UGIEfMzLeWA52713.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Colouring-in Car by Hertz</h3><p>带着小朋友踏上自驾行程时，“我们到了没有？”可能是大人们最常听到的问句（抱怨）了。为了安抚因长途旅行感到无聊烦躁的孩子，汽车租赁公司赫兹推出了一款可以被称为“移动画布”的概念车，将涂色书与车内装饰结合在一起，从座位到天花板都布满了各种各样的图案。目前，这辆车正在赫兹位于伦敦希思罗机场的门店展开试用，<a href=\"http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-4747078/Hertz-unveils-world-s-colouring-car.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">公司表示</a>将会根据用户反馈决定是否正式上线这款车型。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170801184302MzaD7JoWRYQhGUIe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.733198\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170801184259YR1uf0QoSrqsxFXi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.730081\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170801184259P1bGzuTptklhENCy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Kona-shoyu container by nendo</h3><p>京都的怀石料理老店<a href=\"http://www.shimogamosaryo.co.jp/\" rel=\"nofollow\">下鴨茶寮</a>有一种柚子风味的粉末酱油，和普通酱油相比，粉末形态胜在能够让油炸食物保持清脆的口感。最近，日本设计工作室 <a href=\"http://www.nendo.jp/\" rel=\"nofollow\">nendo</a> 受邀为其打造了专用的<a href=\"http://www.nendo.jp/jp/works/kona-shoyu-container/?release\" rel=\"nofollow\">酱油瓶</a>。它的外形借鉴了参拜神社时用来洗手漱口的勺子，便于在倒出时确定分量。如果你对粉酱油感兴趣的话，可以通过<a href=\"http://www.shimogamosaryo.co.jp/shop/products/list.php?category_id=58\" rel=\"nofollow\">官方网站</a>购买，售价从 302 日元起。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170801184314uLKebJWwgrZ0XyOm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667708\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170801184315mAvpZ8u6JtS451fH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667708\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170801184314GJIEWNwvKpQoR1SB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667708\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170801184314FTqVfJdy0b1C7iYU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.336458\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Higher Hangers 2.0 by Drew Cleaver</h3><p>Higher Hangers 的诞生源于设计师 Drew Cleaver 对寝室衣柜的观察：因为衣服挂得不够高，下摆碰到下方的抽屉顶部后都变得皱巴巴的。鉴于无法调整衣柜自带晾衣杆的高度，Cleaver 决定改良衣架的结构，从而省下更多宝贵的衣柜空间。继 2016 年三月推出第一代 Higher Hangers 之后，最近他又带来了迭代版：能够托起衬衣领口的拱形被加强，肩部的轮廓也变得更加饱满。这是它的<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/higherhangers/higher-hangers-20-more-space-less-waste-no-stress\" rel=\"nofollow\">众筹链接</a>，一组 40 个，售价从 39 美元起。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170801184331VGz1uLC3xUFEchdo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563235\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170801184330PwbhEJ2m8uzYetIo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563235\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170801184330PM4EZXLk9SWigY3b.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666176\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>LIFI by Edmundas Jankauskas</h3><p>为了减少食物浪费和塑料垃圾，立陶宛维尔纽斯艺术学院（Vilnius Academy of Arts）的 <a href=\"http://www.creatium.lt/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Edmundas Jankauskas</a> 设计了一个名为 LIFI 的种植系统，让人们能够以更环保的方式自给自足。装有种子的容器由当地树林中采集到的落叶加工制成，只要在顶部做出圆形开口，按照说明加水即可。不同于传统的塑料容器，具有天然气息的 LIFI 还能重复使用，就算直接丢弃也不会造成污染。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170801184349xBGFq8n5kX47TocH.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170801184349erj64BLDVd5kuCsl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170801184349lFt4SuIbXA3jeBGa.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.653000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170801184349jJ6sx0ZEtIbia9lo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Women Talk Real Estate by Baxter and Bailey</h3><p>据统计，在欧洲房地产行业的相关活动上，女性发言人的比例只有 14%，旨在提升行业女性曝光度的非盈利机构 <a href=\"http://womentalkrealestate.org/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Women Talk Real Estate</a> 因此成立，通过建立数据库的方式为活动组织者和从业女性牵线搭桥。英国品牌设计公司 <a href=\"http://www.baxterandbailey.co.uk/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Baxter and Bailey</a> 负责了机构的形象设计，设计团队用麦克风图标取代了机构名，以及上台（on stage）、榜样（role model）这类宣传词中的字母 o，更形象地解释了机构的目标。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170801184405RQ4b3xFhKIE7CfBP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.552000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170801184404YEFdVnpmkRqwIaoe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.119403\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170801184405lTkEgi6xWGFVJHrt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.552000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170801184404NRDIqAdfmLHhac8s.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.119403\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170801184404J5XRC3oi9qAmxF0k.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.119403\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Viva le Vélo by Parallax</h3><p>为了庆祝环法自行车赛 114 岁生日，英国创意公司 <a href=\"https://parall.ax/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Parallax</a> 推出了一个名为 <a href=\"https://parall.ax/viva-le-velo\" rel=\"nofollow\">Viva le Vélo</a> 的网站，回顾了近代著名的八辆参赛自行车以及驾驭它们的车手。身为自行车爱好者的设计总监 Louis Saville 最初只是想为自行车绘制一些有意思的徽标（doodle），直到公司组织的黑客日活动，才决定进一步开发这个项目。当你拖动时间轴查看自行车时，自行车轮就会作出相应的滚动，背景中的年份也会随之跳跃。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170801184453avgE0Q5z8GCo7A2X.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201708011844538aobp7yeRXZJPkKS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170801184454Nybg1O9DWhTxMuC8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170801184454CUqVuf9iTyMQelbj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}